          <p><span class="space-tab"></span>I was born and raised in <a target="_blank" href="https://www.wikiwand.com/en/Addis_Ababa" title="Addis Ababa, Ethiopia">Addis Ababa, Ethiopia</a>, in a town called <a target="_blank" href="https://www.wikiwand.com/en/Kolfe_Keranio" title="">Kolfe Keranio</a>. When I turned eleven, my family and I moved to <a target="_blank" href="https://www.wikiwand.com/en/Githurai" title="Githurai, Kenya">Githurai, Kenya</a> as refugees, and lived there for five years. We relocated to Canada in 2011, where I currently reside. I entered <a target="_blank" href="https://www.wikiwand.com/en/University_of_Waterloo" title="University of Waterloo">University of Waterloo</a> in 2014, studying Mathematics and Computer Science. I started learning to program when I started uni, and web-development in 2015. I am now a full-time student, and part-time web-developer, with a wide range of interests including doing research and working on projects involving AI, robotics, ML/Data-Mining, and a host of other fields.</p>
          <p><span class="space-tab"></span>Some of my hobbies include chess, Rubik's cubes, pi, drawing, football (AKA soccer), martial-arts, cross-country running, and taking strolls in warm sunny days. I am an <a target="_blank" href="https://www.wikiwand.com/en/Ethiopian_Orthodox_Tewahedo_Church" title="EOTC">Ethiopian Orthodox Tewahedo Christian</a>. My favourite food is <a target="_blank" href="https://www.wikiwand.com/en/Injera" title="Most delicious food in the world!">injera</a>, and my favourite song is <a target="_blank" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1UC6ZZGKR3c" title="I'm not going to rickroll you, trust me.">this</a>.</p>
          <p><span class="space-tab"></span>Fun fact: According to my country's <a target="_blank" href="https://www.wikiwand.com/en/Ethiopian_calendar" title="">Ethiopian Calendar</a>, I was born on July 19, 1987, and the current year is 2008. Using the popular <a target="_blank" href="https://www.wikiwand.com/en/Gregorian_calendar" title="">Gregorian Calendar</a>, however, July 26, 1995 is my birthday, and 2016 is the current year.</p>
